visit

public static <Par> long visit(java.lang.Object obj,
                               Visitable.Visitor<Reflect.Fld<java.lang.Object>,Par> vis,
                               Par par)
Calls a visitor for every field of an object, until the visitor returns a negative value.

Type Parameters:
Par - the type of the control parameter
Parameters:
obj - the object
vis - the visitor
par - a control parameter
Returns:
the sum of all non-negative values returned by the visitor, or -1L if an error occurred
